[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63029757]lxlxx911[/uid] (2026-02-05 08:26):[/b]<br/><br/>谷歌财报不是说开支大，利好ai硬件，今天应该先跌后涨吧[/quote]<br/>利好谷歌链硬件 但是又会被中继旭创那些压制  看情况吧 我觉得不是非常大的利好 资金会不会单独冲一个细分很难说，只能说希望<br/>反正如果要买AI硬往谷歌链看肯定会更好", "lou": 685, "content_length": 153, "reply_to": 857038203, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770251328}, {"pid": 857038606, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 08:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857038451,45974302,1209]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60131057]yc419[/uid] (2026-02-05 08:29):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 设备下轨拉满的焚决还管用吗？上班没空看盘 只能买买etf了[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>前提是指数不破位 只要指数没放量跌破4000  我个人觉得没事，个人操作而已啊 不构成投资建议 盈亏自负", "lou": 686, "content_length": 95, "reply_to": 857038451, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770251465}, {"pid": 857038889, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 08:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正前面高点卖过了  我指的是科技类，那今天开盘那个低点我个人肯定不卖的，哪有人高买低卖的 是吧", "lou": 687, "content_length": 90, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770251639}, {"pid": 857041663, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 46, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 08:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857041427,45974302,1211]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43179895]呢个1[/uid] (2026-02-05 08:56):[/b]<br/><br/>年前任何的B都要考虑清楚[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>这句话说的好<br/>要有很高的性价比的B才能下手。这里不是做错了也能被市场带上去的阶段。", "lou": 688, "content_length": 84, "reply_to": 857041427, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770253061}, {"pid": 857048936, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 09:49", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "石油王减了一半石油[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 689, "content_length": 16, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770256191}, {"pid": 857054260, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 10:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202602/05/jmQkub-blxwK4T1kSgo-10.jpg[/img]<br/>不敢睁开眼 希望是我的幻觉<br/>刚才还放量打了一把<br/>我有个不成熟的想法，机构在这里测试GJD还在不在  估计是前面被摁了一周的头有点PTSD了  所以测试一下上下<br/>我目前觉得还行 没有什么恐慌", "lou": 690, "content_length": 201, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202602/05/jmQkub-blxwK4T1kSgo-10.jpg", "size": 5, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202602/05", "name": "jmQkub-blxwK4T1kSgo-10.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770258235}, {"pid": 857054763, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 10:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857054542,45974302,1224]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=6843915]观鱼不语[/uid] (2026-02-05 10:25):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，海峡和平潭又拉起来了，游资另开一桌是不是会抢了航天的资金？[/quote]<br/>航天轮流做双头 不是趋势反转  不受影响的。", "lou": 691, "content_length": 43, "reply_to": 857054542, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770258416}, {"pid": 857055644, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 10:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857055078,45974302,1225]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1003090]zzh90pk[/uid] (2026-02-05 10:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大可以咨询下今天你跌的比率不高是靠做t还是仓位控制达成的吗？<br/>主仓在科技跌麻了全仓5个点，看到你这个跌幅惊为天人。。。[/quote]<br/>我做超跌修复的打野很多。没行情肯定要做没行情的操作 我早上亮了ETF持仓你们就应该懂了 当然 不是今天才减的 <br/>应该是这段时间最高点减的  而且还招呼了大家，但是发现还是很多人不信 <br/>没关系 我也不是全对的。市场才是对的", "lou": 692, "content_length": 202, "reply_to": 857055078, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770258707}, {"pid": 857055807, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-05 10: